---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - TaxPortal" description="TaxPortal privacy policy. Learn how we protect your data and ensure your privacy.">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-canvas dark:bg-primary">
    <main class="min-h-screen">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-ink mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-6 text-body dark:text-muted">
          <p>Last updated: July 2026</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>TaxPortal does not require you to create an account or provide personal information to use our calculators and guides. We do not collect, store, or share any personal data.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">Calculations Performed Locally</h2>
          <p>All tax calculations are performed directly in your browser. No calculation data is sent to our servers or stored anywhere.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
          <p>We use local storage only to remember your language preference and theme choice. We do not use tracking cookies or third-party analytics.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>Our site contains links to official government tax authority websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of external sites.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please reach out through our contact channels.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
